{"tid":36856,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍心理質素訓練　士兵傳炸藥「練膽」","createTime":"2016-12-13T03:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T04:05:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb994b2016bbeb38b51d4e39fbb394211c20a2ec","tid":36856,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161213/photo/bkncn-20161213060525223-1213_05011_001_03p.jpg?20161213072428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161213%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161213060525223-1213_05011_001_03p.jpg%3F20161213072428&h=81049098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n士兵需在10秒內傳完炸藥包。（電視畫面）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161213/photo/bkncn-20161213060525223-1213_05011_001_04p.jpg?20161213072428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161213%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161213060525223-1213_05011_001_04p.jpg%3F20161213072428&h=b01ca7ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n士兵以各種姿勢進行信任射擊訓練。（電視畫面）<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=tixlDIhp708RpPAu63cKmwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=62ab0210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】解放軍陸軍第14集團軍某裝甲旅近日在模擬戰場環境下進行了一次心理質素綜合訓練，內容包括坦克過頂、射擊演習和傳遞炸藥包等項目。據了解，該次訓練旨在加強士兵的抗衝擊能力、心理承受能力，以增強他們在實戰時的戰鬥力和適應性。 <br />\n<br />\n內地官媒報道，參與士兵需在坦克過頂訓練中，從側面追越前方坦克，然後躺在坦克正前方，任由坦克從自己身上「零距離」地駛過。另外，士兵也進行了信任射擊訓練，以平躺、跪地、站立等姿勢體驗戰場環境，從而克服對槍林彈雨的恐懼感。 <br />\n<br />\n該次訓練也進行了炸藥包傳遞的演習。士兵需傳遞一包由2公斤TNT炸藥構成的炸藥包，威力相當於400個手榴彈同時爆炸；由於導火線的安全燃燒時間僅為10秒，8名士兵便需挑戰在10秒內傳完炸藥包。"},{"pid":"e3f1a3fa24f49e425c5c0c94aae8deb8f7b803e0","tid":36856,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"反正唔識爆，有咩好驚？"},{"pid":"46e8da838dc1fbb55db3aa0eaa2b22e58c34930c","tid":36856,"uid":63853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:46:00.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯練膽大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88c04defbaba0a84167cb79e37a312c0733e1e7","tid":36856,"uid":50890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:46:17.000Z","msg":"你戴頭盔不突止重着埋避彈衣？你個冚家鏟！"},{"pid":"be5b4b4c68da82638ee0de788d1da47cb473d1b4","tid":36856,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:47:08.000Z","msg":"炸彈果個兩次都係剪接嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483275e611975cb4d8b4185770902a94de6429b8","tid":36856,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"197858e0286efda8fabd0028306c3f64b35b3580","tid":36856,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:49:13.000Z","msg":"好似有聲"},{"pid":"5f01ebf3c313a8591a9f1c19c3f5657ab5668472","tid":36856,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果講心理質素訓練好似北韓果d神打仲有效"},{"pid":"a447b21bb8d1d7dcfa33b854b4ec4ccf2160ab3d","tid":36856,"uid":59722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"根本係回魂夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f2e2e1d1d5e15cd716c1fd1ac80e591d33019b","tid":36856,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:00:52.000Z","msg":"無用口咬住炸彈邊算練大膽呀"},{"pid":"205ed3f7f6d0c1793ab5cce7971c57d0a5fc1ea2","tid":36856,"uid":12393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯練膽大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298cfe13c3f98d6efa846c4de0012b69d2c19036","tid":36856,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:05:59.0